window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>I was a just normal guy until the night the cherry blossoms bloomed, the night that Grace appeared on my doorstep. A failed sci-fi writer, a gamer, but a normal guy nonetheless. Grace was everything I was not, a psychic shifter, beautiful beyond my wildest imagination, a government conspiracy <br> waiting to be unraveled. And that was before the second superpowered woman showed up to kill us both. </p>"; 
